>Snack, Nut and Crisp Manufacturers’ Association</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">SPA</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Soya Protein Association</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">SSA</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Seasoning and Spice Association</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">UKAMBY</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">UK</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> Association of Manufacturers of Bakers’ Yeast</span><br /><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">UKHIA</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">UK</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> Herbal Infusions Association</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">UKTC</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">UK</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> Tea Council</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">FDF also runs specialist sector groups for members:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">BCCC</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Biscuit, Cake, Chocolate and Confectionery Group</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">FF</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Frozen Food Group</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">MG</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Meat Group</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">ORG</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Organic Group</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">SG</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Seafood Group</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt; font-weight:bold">              </span></p></div><hr style="width:33%; height:1px; text-align:left" /><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn1"></a><a href="#_ftnref1">[1]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><a href="http://www.bis.gov.uk/assets/bispartners/foresight/docs/food-and-farming/11-546-future-of-food-and-farming-report.pdf"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; text